{"title":"建机房","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":15,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3724","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"\">这个星期三，日本人要来鸟市x中视查，主要是看看曾经送给x中的计算机是否还在用。其实这些计</span></p><p><span style=\"\">算机早都被淘汰了，不过为了应付他们，计算机竞赛小组还是需要把这个机房建起来。可是，在</span></p><p><span style=\"\">机房的建设过程中，出了一点小问题：网线不够长。可是为了把机房建好，就必须把这些计算机</span></p><p><span style=\"\">都连接起来，所以，需要计算把所有的计算机连起来需要多长的网线。</span> </p><p><span style=\"\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"\">由于计算机很多，用手算很费时间，现在就找来了正在竞赛集训的你，你的任务是遍程序计算把</span></p><p><span style=\"\">所有的计算机连起来需要多长的网线。</span> </p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">第</span><span style=\"\">2</span><span style=\"\">～</span><span style=\"\">n+1</span><span style=\"\">行：一个邻接矩阵，告诉你每两台计算机的距离。当然，对角线将会是</span><span style=\"\">0</span><span style=\"\">，因为不会有</span></p><p><span style=\"\">计算机和自己相连。每个数字不超过</span><span style=\"\">100000</span><span style=\"\">。</span></p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:新宋体\">一行：把所有的计算机连起来需要的最短的网线。</span> </p><p><br/></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">4 </span></p><p><span style=\"\">0 4 9 21 </span></p><p><span style=\"\">4 0 8 17 </span></p><p><span style=\"\">9 8 0 16 </span></p><p><span style=\"\">21 17 16 0 </span></p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>28</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">3&lt;=n&lt;=100</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}